WWW-BugMeNot version 0.01
=========================

Many websites require compulsory registration before they will allow readers to access their pages. This is bad for a variety of reasons, and so many people use BugMeNot.com to share common usernames and passwords. This module provides a programmatic interface to BugMeNot. It takes a URL, and returns a username/password pair, as per the BugMeNot site.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::Simple
  HTML::TokeParser

